The Shirehorses are a spoof band comprising two BBC Radio DJs from [MASK], Mark Radcliffe and Marc Riley, known collectively as Mark and Lard.As part of their BBC Radio 1 shows, the pair produced pastiches of chart songs, such as "You're Gormless", a parody of Babybird's "You're Gorgeous", "Lardy Boy", a parody of Placebo's "Nancy Boy", and "Why Is It Always Dairylea", spoofing Travis's "Why Does It Always Rain on Me?
